00:10:31,960 --> 00:10:36,440
are opened, the water comes crashing down and it hits the area

195
00:10:36,440 --> 00:10:39,840
directly below it. Person isn't there in the area directly below it.

196
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:44,100
After the water hits that area of the floor directly below it,

197
00:10:44,160 --> 00:10:48,600
it then continues to move on and then it drowns the person

198
00:10:48,600 --> 00:10:51,420
who is standing a few feet back. So there what we say

199
00:10:51,420 --> 00:10:55,200
is, when I removed the sluice gates, the crashing down of the

200
00:10:55,200 --> 00:10:58,480
water, that was like I had shot that arrow. I had made

201
00:10:58,480 --> 00:11:02,040
that water crash down. I had thrown that water. That hit the

202
00:11:02,040 --> 00:11:04,480
base, and that hit the base. If he was at the base,

203
00:11:04,540 --> 00:11:07,340
I would have thrown the water on him effectively and killed him.

204
00:11:07,600 --> 00:11:10,680
But he wasn't at the base; he was ten feet away. So

205
00:11:10,680 --> 00:11:13,280
I threw the water down at the base, and then the water

206
00:11:13,280 --> 00:11:17,720
moved and it killed him afterwards. That was not my energy; that

207
00:11:17,720 --> 00:11:22,120
was a derivative of my energy, and therefore I am not חייב.

208
00:11:21,520 --> 00:11:26,020
chayav. So this is a pretty amazing idea. Obviously I caused his

209
00:11:26,020 --> 00:11:29,880
death, but in הלכה, halacha, both for murder and even for issues

210
00:11:29,880 --> 00:11:33,960
of נזק nezek damages, it's not about causation, it's about the action

211
00:11:33,960 --> 00:11:38,020
itself. And since this is not my energy but something that derived

212
00:11:38,020 --> 00:11:40,880
from it, a כוח שני, koach sheni, I am going to be

213
00:11:41,000 --> 00:11:45,880
exempt. So this becomes a very interesting and important halachic concept for

214
00:11:45,880 --> 00:11:49,440
many areas about defining what is considered to be my act and

215
00:11:49,440 --> 00:11:54,300
not my act in a way, although it's obviously troubling to say

216
00:11:54,300 --> 00:11:57,140
that I would be exempt although the guy dies just because he's

217
00:11:57,140 --> 00:12:00,440
a few feet away, and that's a separate discussion. And the רמב״ם

218
00:12:00,200 --> 00:12:02,640
Rambam makes a special point, the גמרא Gemara makes a special point

219
00:12:02,640 --> 00:12:05,780
about חייב בדיני שמיים, chayav b'dinei shamayim, that I'm obviously liable as

220
00:12:05,780 --> 00:12:07,680
far as heaven is concerned and maybe the court would have a

221
00:12:07,680 --> 00:12:11,020
way of dealing with me if not through a formal process. But

222
00:12:11,020 --> 00:12:13,880
what is more sort of interesting for us is that even when

223
00:12:13,880 --> 00:12:16,880
it is demanded that I do an action, I don't have to

224
00:12:16,880 --> 00:12:21,680
be providing the energy itself; if I release energy, then the initial

225
00:12:21,680 --> 00:12:26,240
impact is considered to be mine as well. So here too, if

226
00:12:26,240 --> 00:12:29,140
I have a water wheel and I release the energy of the

227
00:12:29,140 --> 00:12:32,920
water, I open up the gate that allows the river to rush

228
00:12:32,920 --> 00:12:36,760
through, that initial turning of the wheel that comes through the energy

229
00:12:36,760 --> 00:12:41,400
I immediately release, that would actually be considered my action. As the

230
00:12:41,400 --> 00:12:44,860
river continues to push the wheel, then it's just happening on its

231
00:12:44,860 --> 00:12:48,880
own, it's no longer my energy, but that original push is considered

232
00:12:48,880 --> 00:12:51,860
to be כוח ראשון koach rishon and is considered to be my

233
00:12:51,860 --> 00:12:53,700
energy. So this is

234
00:12:55,100 --> 00:12:57,080
relevant for a number of issues. For example,

235
00:12:59,040 --> 00:13:02,560
describing the difference between action and גרמא. grama. So for example, let's

236
00:13:02,560 --> 00:13:06,480
talk about turning on the lights on שבת. Shabbat. So let's assume

237
00:13:06,480 --> 00:13:10,060
for argument's sake that an incandescent light is אש. esh. It heats

238
00:13:10,060 --> 00:13:13,440
up a piece of metal, it causes it to glow; that, let's

239
00:13:13,440 --> 00:13:16,720
assume that that is generally assumed that that is אש. esh. Now,

240
00:13:16,860 --> 00:13:19,660
do I actually heat up that piece of metal? Well, if you

241
00:13:19,660 --> 00:13:22,220
look at what I do at a micro level, what I actually

242
00:13:22,220 --> 00:13:25,620
do is I close a circuit by switching the light, and because

243
00:13:25,620 --> 00:13:30,380
I close a circuit, that then leads to the electrons moving and

244
00:13:30,380 --> 00:13:33,900
ultimately going into that piece of metal and heating it up and

245
00:13:33,900 --> 00:13:36,920
causing the light to go on. Of course this happens so instantaneously

246
00:13:36,920 --> 00:13:40,880
that we're not aware of the time lapse, but effectively I did

247
00:13:40,880 --> 00:13:44,000
not heat that piece of metal; I closed a circuit and then,

248
00:13:44,280 --> 00:13:49,200
if you would, the water, the electrons rushed through this closed circuit

249
00:13:49,200 --> 00:13:53,720
and heated up that piece of metal. So in general, this we

250
00:13:53,720 --> 00:13:56,880
consider this to not be גרמא, grama, we consider this to be

251
00:13:56,880 --> 00:13:57,100
מעשה ma'aseh

252
00:13:58,120 --> 00:14:01,260
for exactly the reason here of the sluice gates. I did it,

253
00:14:01,460 --> 00:14:05,460
it happened immediately, so the immediacy is relevant, and because it happened

254
00:14:05,460 --> 00:14:09,600
immediately, it is considered like I actually did the thing itself, like

255
00:14:09,600 --> 00:14:15,280
I turned on the light itself. So here's an interesting example לחומרא

256
00:14:14,860 --> 00:14:18,400
l'chumra where it's important to say that גרמא, grama, although it can

257
00:14:18,400 --> 00:14:21,640
be broken down into stages and it's not my energy, when it's

258
00:14:21,640 --> 00:14:25,480
an immediate result and I'm like releasing some power, it's considered like

259
00:14:25,480 --> 00:14:29,100
I did it. Interesting other cases to ask about in general are

