you don't need כוח גברא, koach gavra, you more need כוונה, kavana,

266
00:14:46,280 --> 00:14:49,480
but here it seems very clearly that at least what happens afterwards,

267
00:14:49,600 --> 00:14:53,520
after the initial spurt, that is not considered my direct action, that's

268
00:14:53,520 --> 00:14:54,000
considered my

269
00:14:59,680 --> 00:15:02,640
גרמא. grama. another criteria by שחיטה, shechita, which is called כוח גברא,

